{
  "page": "Grazdan (spiked beard)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For other characters with the same name, see <a href=\"/index.php/Grazdan_(disambiguation)\" title=\"Grazdan (disambiguation)\">Grazdan (disambiguation)</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Grazdan</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Good_Masters\" title=\"Good Masters\">Good Masters</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Astapor\" title=\"Astapor\">Astapori</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299&#160;AC</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Astapor\" title=\"Astapor\">Astapor</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (appears)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Grazdan</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Good_Masters\" title=\"Good Masters\">Good Master</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Astapor\" title=\"Astapor\">Astapor</a>. He was presumably named after <a href=\"/index.php/Grazdan_the_Great\" title=\"Grazdan the Great\">Grazdan the Great</a>, who founded <a href=\"/index.php/Old_Ghis\" title=\"Old Ghis\">Old Ghis</a>. He has a spiked beard, and speaks the <a href=\"/index.php/Common_Tongue\" title=\"Common Tongue\">Common Tongue</a>, though not well.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Grazdan_(spiked_beard)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Grazdan_(spiked_beard)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Grazdan is among the Good Masters who bargain with <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> over how many <a href=\"/index.php/Unsullied\" title=\"Unsullied\">Unsullied</a> she could purchase. He offers her two thousand. He is present when Daenerys buys her Unsullied, and is the one who demands <a href=\"/index.php/Drogon\" title=\"Drogon\">Drogon</a> to be turned over. He is also present during the <a href=\"/index.php/Sack_of_Astapor\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sack of Astapor\">Sack of Astapor</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Grazdan_(spiked_beard)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_27\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 27\">Chapter 27</a>, Daenerys III.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403094643\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.081 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.299 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 560/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10468/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 3975/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 286/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 809/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.190/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.65 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  293.158      1 -total\n 83.89%  245.923      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 83.22%  243.967      1 Template:Infobox\n 13.64%   39.993      1 Template:For\n 10.86%   31.834     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  3.25%    9.517      3 Template:Infobox_label\n  1.90%    5.562      2 Template:Ref\n  1.33%    3.887      1 Template:Date\n  1.31%    3.847      2 Template:Ref/core\n  0.47%    1.381      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:23257-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403094643 and revision id 316110\n -->\n",
